Package: rustafits
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libcfitsio9
Description: High-performance FITS to JPEG converter
 FITS to JPEG converter for astronomical images with QuickFits/PixInsight-
 compatible auto-stretch and Bayer debayering.
 .
 Features:
  * Auto-Stretch: Median-based statistical stretching (robust to outliers)
  * Bayer Debayering: Super-pixel 2×2 block averaging
  * Preview Mode: 2×2 binning for mono images (4× fewer pixels)
  * Fast: 60-100ms for 4096×4096 images
  * Multi-Platform SIMD: ARM NEON + x86_64 SSE2
